## Domain Boundaries

When modifying code, stay within your domain boundary. The domains and their files are defined in `docs/system-manifest.yaml` under `domains:`. Key rule: **do NOT modify files outside your domain's file list without explicit approval.**

## Quality Over Speed

The goal of this process is meticulous system evolution with minimized problems — NOT maximum deployment velocity. Frame every decision around problem prevention, not throughput.
